// ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ SORTABLE STYLE CARD ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ

interface StyleCardProps {
    style: CommentStyleConfig
    onUpdate: (updates: Partial<CommentStyleConfig>) => void
    onDuplicate: () => void
    onReset: () => void
    onDelete: () => void
    isNew?: boolean
}

function SortableStyleCard({
    style,
    onUpdate,
    onDuplicate,
    onReset,
    onDelete,
    isNew
}: StyleCardProps) {
    const {
        attributes,
        listeners,
        setNodeRef,
        transform,
        transition,
        isDragging
    } = useSortable({ id: style.id })

    const dndStyle = {
        transform: CSS.Transform.toString(transform),
        transition,
        zIndex: isDragging ? 10 : 1,
    }

    const [prompt, setPrompt] = useState(style.prompt)
    const [isSaving, setIsSaving] = useState(false)
    const timerRef = useRef<NodeJS.Timeout | null>(null)

    // Token counter estimation (1 token ‚âà 4 chars)
    const tokens = Math.ceil(prompt.length / 4)

    const handlePromptChange = (val: string) => {
        setPrompt(val)

        if (timerRef.current) clearTimeout(timerRef.current)

        setIsSaving(true)
        timerRef.current = setTimeout(() => {
            onUpdate({ prompt: val })
            setIsSaving(false)
            toast.success('‚úì Salvo', {
                duration: 1500,
                position: 'bottom-center',
                className: 'text-[11px] font-bold bg-linkedflow-bg border-linkedflow-border h-8'
            })
        }, 800)
    }

    return (
        <motion.div
            ref={setNodeRef}
            style={dndStyle}
            initial={isNew ? { opacity: 0, y: 20 } : false}
            animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
            layout
            className={cn(
                "bg-linkedflow-s1 border border-linkedflow-border rounded-2xl p-4 mb-3 transition-shadow",
                isDragging && "opacity-50 scale-[1.01] shadow-xl border-linkedflow-accent/40",
                !style.active && "opacity-60"
            )}
        >
            {/* Header */}
            <div className="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                <button
                    {...attributes}
                    {...listeners}
                    className="cursor-grab active:cursor-grabbing p-1 text-linkedflow-text3 hover:text-linkedflow-text transition-colors"
                >
                    <GripVertical size={18} />
                </button>

                <input
                    type="text"
                    value={style.icon}
                    onChange={(e) => onUpdate({ icon: e.target.value.slice(0, 2) })}
                    className="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center bg-linkedflow-s2 border border-linkedflow-border rounded-xl text-lg text-center focus:border-linkedflow-accent focus:ring-0 outline-none"
                />

                <div className="flex-1">
                    <input
                        type="text"
                        value={style.label}
                        onChange={(e) => onUpdate({ label: e.target.value })}
                        className="bg-transparent border-none border-b border-transparent focus:border-linkedflow-accent outline-none text-[14px] font-bold text-linkedflow-text w-full transition-all"
                        placeholder="Nome do estilo"
                    />
                    <div className="flex items-center gap-2 mt-0.5">
                        <AnimatePresence mode="wait">
                            {style.active ? (
                                <motion.span
                                    key="active"
                                    initial={{ opacity: 0, scale: 0.8 }}
                                    animate={{ opacity: 1, scale: 1 }}
                                    className="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider font-bold text-linkedflow-green flex items-center gap-1"
                                >
                                    <Check size={10} /> Ativo
                                </motion.span>
                            ) : (
                                <motion.span
                                    key="inactive"
                                    initial={{ opacity: 0, scale: 0.8 }}
                                    animate={{ opacity: 1, scale: 1 }}
                                    className="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider font-bold text-linkedflow-text3"
                                >
                                    Inativo
                                </motion.span>
                            )}
                        </AnimatePresence>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div className="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <Switch
                        checked={style.active}
                        onCheckedChange={(checked) => onUpdate({ active: checked })}
                    />

                    <DropdownMenu>
                        <DropdownMenuTrigger asChild>
                            <Button variant="ghost" size="icon" className="h-8 w-8 text-linkedflow-text3 hover:text-linkedflow-text">
                                <MoreHorizontal size={18} />
                            </Button>
                        </DropdownMenuTrigger>
                        <DropdownMenuContent align="end" className="bg-linkedflow-s1 border-linkedflow-border">
                            <DropdownMenuItem onClick={onReset} className="text-[13px] gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-linkedflow-s2">
                                <RotateCcw size={14} /> Restaurar padr√£o
                            </DropdownMenuItem>
                            <DropdownMenuItem onClick={onDuplicate} className="text-[13px] gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-linkedflow-s2">
                                <Copy size={14} /> Duplicar estilo
                            </DropdownMenuItem>
                            <DropdownMenuItem onClick={onDelete} className="text-[13px] gap-2 cursor-pointer text-red-500 hover:bg-red-500/10 focus:text-red-500">
                                <Trash2 size={14} /> Excluir
                            </DropdownMenuItem>
                        </DropdownMenuContent>
                    </DropdownMenu>
                </div>
            </div>

            {/* Box do Prompt */}
            <div className="space-y-1.5 p-1">
                <div className="flex items-center justify-between">
                    <label className="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold text-linkedflow-text3">
                        Prompt enviado √† IA
                    </label>
                    {isSaving && (
                        <span className="text-[10px] text-linkedflow-accent animate-pulse font-medium">Sincronizando...</span>
                    )}
                </div>
                <div className="relative group">
                    <Textarea
                        value={prompt}
                        onChange={(e) => handlePromptChange(e.target.value)}
                        className="bg-linkedflow-s2 border-linkedflow-border rounded-xl py-3 px-4 text-[13px] text-linkedflow-text2 leading-relaxed min-h-[120px] focus:border-linkedflow-accent focus:ring-0 resize-none transition-colors"
                        placeholder="Ex: Escreva uma resposta curta e motivadora..."
                    />
                    <div className="absolute bottom-3 right-3 text-[10px] text-linkedflow-text3 font-medium bg-linkedflow-s1/60 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded backdrop-blur-sm">
                        ~{tokens} tokens
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            {/* Footer Info */}
            <div className="mt-4 pt-3 border-t border-linkedflow-border/50 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-3">
                <div className="flex-1">
                    <label className="text-[10px] text-linkedflow-text3 uppercase font-bold block mb-1">Descri√ß√£o curta</label>
                    <input
                        type="text"
                        value={style.description}
                        onChange={(e) => onUpdate({ description: e.target.value })}
                        placeholder="Ex: Ideal para celebrar vit√≥rias"
                        className="bg-transparent border-none text-[12px] text-linkedflow-text2 placeholder:text-linkedflow-text3/50 w-full outline-none focus:text-linkedflow-text"
                    />
                </div>
                <div className="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 bg-linkedflow-s2/50 rounded-lg border border-linkedflow-border">
                    <span className="text-[10px] text-linkedflow-text3 font-medium">Preview:</span>
                    <div className="flex items-center gap-1.5">
                        <span className="text-sm">{style.icon}</span>
                        <span className="text-[12px] font-bold text-linkedflow-text">{style.label}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </motion.div>
    )
}

// ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ MAIN PROMPTS EDITOR PAGE ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ

export function PromptsEditor() {
    const styles = useSettingsStore((s) => s.commentStyles)
    const reorderStyles = useSettingsStore((s) => s.reorderStyles)
    const updateStyle = useSettingsStore((s) => s.updateCommentStyle)
    const addStyle = useSettingsStore((s) => s.addCommentStyle)
    const duplicateStyle = useSettingsStore((s) => s.duplicateStyle)
    const resetStyle = useSettingsStore((s) => s.resetStyleToDefault)
    const resetAllStyles = useSettingsStore((s) => s.resetAllStylesToDefault)
    const removeStyle = useSettingsStore((s) => s.removeCommentStyle)

    const [confirmReset, setConfirmReset] = useState(false)
    const lastAddedId = useRef<string | null>(null)

    const sensors = useSensors(
        useSensor(PointerSensor),
        useSensor(KeyboardSensor, {
            coordinateGetter: sortableKeyboardCoordinates,
        })
    )

    const handleDragEnd = (event: DragEndEvent) => {
        const { active, over } = event
        if (active.id !== over?.id) {
            reorderStyles(active.id as string, over?.id as string)
        }
    }

    const handleAddNew = () => {
        const newId = `custom_${Date.now()}`
        const newStyle: CommentStyleConfig = {
            id: newId as CommentStyleId,
            label: 'Novo Estilo',
            icon: 'üí¨',
            description: 'Personalize como quiser',
            prompt: '',
            active: true,
            order: styles.length
        }
        lastAddedId.current = newId
        addStyle(newStyle)
        toast.success('Estilo criado!')
    }

    return (
        <div className="max-w-4xl mx-auto w-full px-6 py-10">
            {/* Header P√°gina */}
            <div className="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between mb-10 gap-4">
                <div>
                    <h2 className="font-bricolage text-3xl font-bold text-linkedflow-text tracking-tight">
                        Estilos de Resposta
                    </h2>
                    <p className="text-[14px] text-linkedflow-text3 mt-1.5 max-w-lg leading-relaxed">
                        Reordene, edite ou crie novos comportamentos para a intelig√™ncia artificial. Arraste os cart√µes para mudar a ordem no feed.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div className="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <AnimatePresence mode="wait">
                        {confirmReset ? (
                            <motion.div
                                initial={{ opacity: 0, x: 10 }}
                                animate={{ opacity: 1, x: 0 }}
                                exit={{ opacity: 0, x: -10 }}
                                className="flex items-center gap-2 bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-xl"
                            >
                                <span className="text-[11px] font-bold text-red-500 uppercase">Tem certeza?</span>
                                <Button
                                    variant="ghost"
                                    size="sm"
                                    className="h-8 text-[11px] font-bold text-red-500 hover:bg-red-500 hover:text-white rounded-lg"
                                    onClick={() => {
                                        resetAllStyles()
                                        setConfirmReset(false)
                                        toast.success('Padr√µes restaurados')
                                    }}
                                >
                                    Sim
                                </Button>
                                <Button
                                    variant="ghost"
                                    size="sm"
                                    className="h-8 text-[11px] font-bold text-red-500 hover:bg-red-500/5 rounded-lg"
                                    onClick={() => setConfirmReset(false)}
                                >
                                    N√£o
                                </Button>
                            </motion.div>
                        ) : (
                            <Button
                                variant="ghost"
                                onClick={() => setConfirmReset(true)}
                                className="text-linkedflow-text3 hover:text-red-400 hover:bg-red-400/10 text-[12px] font-bold rounded-xl h-10 px-4"
                            >
                                Restaurar Tudo
                            </Button>
                        )}
                    </AnimatePresence>

                    <Button
                        onClick={handleAddNew}
                        className="bg-linkedflow-accent hover:bg-linkedflow-accent/90 text-white font-bold rounded-xl h-10 px-6 shadow-lg shadow-linkedflow-accent/20"
                    >
                        <Plus size={18} className="mr-2" />
                        Novo Estilo
                    </Button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div className="bg-linkedflow-accent/5 border border-linkedflow-accent/20 rounded-2xl p-4 mb-8 flex gap-3 items-start animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-top-2 duration-500">
                <HelpCircle className="text-linkedflow-accent h-5 w-5 shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                <div className="text-[13px] text-linkedflow-text2 leading-relaxed">
                    <strong>Variables:</strong> Use tags como <code className="bg-linkedflow-accent/10 px-1 rounded text-linkedflow-accent">{"{postText}"}</code> ou <code className="bg-linkedflow-accent/10 px-1 rounded text-linkedflow-accent">{"{authorName}"}</code> no seu prompt. O sistema far√° a substitui√ß√£o autom√°tica no momento da gera√ß√£o.
                </div>
            </div>

            {/* Lista Sortable */}
            <DndContext
                sensors={sensors}
                collisionDetection={closestCenter}
                onDragEnd={handleDragEnd}
                modifiers={[restrictToVerticalAxis]}
            >
                <SortableContext
                    items={styles.map(s => s.id)}
                    strategy={verticalListSortingStrategy}
                >
                    <div className="flex flex-col">
                        <AnimatePresence mode="popLayout">
                            {styles.map((style) => (
                                <SortableStyleCard
                                    key={style.id}
                                    style={style}
                                    isNew={style.id === lastAddedId.current}
                                    onUpdate={(updates) => updateStyle(style.id, updates)}
                                    onDuplicate={() => duplicateStyle(style.id)}
                                    onReset={() => {
                                        resetStyle(style.id)
                                        toast.success('Prompt original restaurado')
                                    }}
                                    onDelete={() => {
                                        removeStyle(style.id)
                                        toast.error('Estilo removido')
                                    }}
                                />
                            ))}
                        </AnimatePresence>
                    </div>
                </SortableContext>
            </DndContext>

            {styles.length === 0 && (
                <div className="flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-20 border-2 border-dashed border-linkedflow-border rounded-3xl opacity-50">
                    <AlertCircle size={40} className="text-linkedflow-text3 mb-4" />
                    <p className="text-[15px] font-medium text-linkedflow-text3">Nenhum estilo configurado</p>
                    <Button variant="link" onClick={handleAddNew} className="text-linkedflow-accent font-bold mt-2">Adicionar o primeiro</Button>
                </div>
            )}
        </div>
    )
}

import { db, monitoredProfiles } from '@/db'
import { eq, and, asc, desc } from 'drizzle-orm'
import type { NewMonitoredProfile } from '@/db/schema/profiles'

// Busca todos os perfis de um usu√°rio, ordenados por displayOrder
export async function getProfilesByUser(userId: string) {
    return db
        .select()
        .from(monitoredProfiles)
        .where(eq(monitoredProfiles.userId, userId))
        .orderBy(asc(monitoredProfiles.displayOrder))
}

// Apenas perfis ativos (para o feed)
export async function getActiveProfilesByUser(userId: string) {
    return db
        .select()
        .from(monitoredProfiles)
        .where(
            and(
                eq(monitoredProfiles.userId, userId),
                eq(monitoredProfiles.active, true)
            )
        )
        .orderBy(asc(monitoredProfiles.displayOrder))
}

export async function getProfileById(id: string) {
    const [profile] = await db
        .select()
        .from(monitoredProfiles)
        .where(eq(monitoredProfiles.id, id))
        .limit(1)
    return profile ?? null
}

export async function createProfile(data: NewMonitoredProfile) {
    const [profile] = await db
        .insert(monitoredProfiles)
        .values(data)
        .returning()
    return profile
}

export async function updateProfile(
    id: string,
    data: Partial<NewMonitoredProfile>
) {
    const [updated] = await db
        .update(monitoredProfiles)
        .set({ ...data, updatedAt: new Date() })
        .where(eq(monitoredProfiles.id, id))
        .returning()
    return updated
}

export async function toggleProfileActive(id: string, active: boolean) {
    return updateProfile(id, { active })
}

export async function deleteProfile(id: string) {
    await db
        .delete(monitoredProfiles)
        .where(eq(monitoredProfiles.id, id))
}

// Reordena perfis: recebe array de { id, order }
export async function reorderProfiles(
    userId: string,
    order: Array<{ id: string; displayOrder: number }>
) {
    await db.transaction(async (tx) => {
        await Promise.all(
            order.map(({ id, displayOrder }) =>
                tx
                    .update(monitoredProfiles)
                    .set({ displayOrder, updatedAt: new Date() })
                    .where(
                        and(
                            eq(monitoredProfiles.id, id),
                            eq(monitoredProfiles.userId, userId)
                        )
                    )
            )
        )
    })
}

